<section class="band"><div class="shell">
  <p class="eyebrow">After checkout</p>
  <h2>What happens after you buy a kit.</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <article class="card"><h3>Stripe verifies payment</h3><p>Checkout sends the product SKU and optional discount code to Stripe, then returns you to ApprovalPrep after payment.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Files unlock</h3><p>Every paid product is a direct paid download. You get the PDF guide for reference and the editable DOCX kit with fill-in placeholders.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>Choose how to fill it</h3><p>Fill the DOCX yourself, or use the free browser-only Studio to create a prefilled first-pass draft. The Studio is optional and does not store your answers.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><h3>You stay in control</h3><p>ApprovalPrep does not store your letter answers or send anything for you. You review, edit, download, and send your own materials.</p></article>
  </div>
</div></section>
